      </span>
      <span class="ticker-item">
        AS A TRUSTED BATHROOM REMODELING COMPANY IN MARYLAND, OUR TEAM KNOWS THAT EVERY PROJECT STARTS WITH A CLEAR PLAN, HIGH-QUALITY MATERIALS, AND A DESIGN BUILT AROUND YOUR NEEDS&nbsp;&nbsp;
      </span>
    </div>
  </div>

  <div class="kitchen-remodeling-info-row">
    <div class="kitchen-remodeling-info-image">
      <Image
        src={Img2}
        alt="Kitchen design inspiration"
      />
    </div>
    <div class="kitchen-remodeling-info-content">
      <h2 class="kitchen-remodeling-info-title">
        How We Approach Bathroom Remodeling
      </h2>
      <p class="kitchen-remodeling-info-paragraph">
        A well-designed bathroom is more than just a space — it's a personal retreat. We begin by understanding your goals, style preferences, and functional needs.
        <br /><br />
        From layout planning and bathroom design solutions to plumbing upgrades, lighting, flooring, and tile work, every element is chosen and installed with care by our expert team.
        <br /><br />
        Whether you prefer sleek and modern or warm and classic, we deliver custom bathroom remodels with exceptional craftsmanship and attention to detail.
      </p>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>


<style>

  @import url("https://fonts.googleapis.com/css2?family=DM+Sans:ital,opsz,wght@0,9..40,100..1000;1,9..40,100..1000&family=Host+Grotesk:ital,wght@0,300..800;1,300..800&display=swap");

  .kitchen-remodeling-section-container {
    background-color: #ffffff;
    padding: 80px 0;
    font-family: 'DM Sans', Arial, sans-serif; 
    color: #333333;
    box-sizing: border-box;
  }

  .kitchen-remodeling-content-wrapper {
    display: flex;
    margin: 0 auto;
    padding: 0 40px; 
    gap: 80px; 
    align-items: flex-end;
    box-sizing: border-box;
  }

  .kitchen-remodeling-text-column {
    flex: 1;
    max-width: 50%; 
    display: flex; 
    flex-direction: column;
    align-items: flex-start; 
  }

  .kitchen-remodeling-title {
    font-size: 6em; 
    margin-top: 0;
    color: #000000;
    display: block;
    width: 700px;
    margin-right: -400px;
    z-index: 100;
    margin-bottom: 50px;
    font-family: "Host Grotesk", sans-serif;
    font-weight: 600;
    line-height: 1.2;
    word-break: break-word; 
  }

  .kitchen-remodeling-paragraph {
    font-size: 14px;
    margin-bottom: 20px;
    color: #555555;
    line-height: 1.6;
  }

  .kitchen-remodeling-list {
    list-style: none;
    padding: 0;
  }

  .kitchen-remodeling-list li {
    font-size: 14px;
    margin-bottom: 10px;
    position: relative;
    padding-left: 20px;
    color: #555555;
    line-height: 1.5; 
  }

  .kitchen-remodeling-list li::before {
    content: "";
    display: block;
    width: 6px;
    height: 6px;
    background-color: #000000;
    border-radius: 50%;
    position: absolute;
    left: 0;
    top: 0.7em; 
  }

  .kitchen-remodeling-paragraph.last-paragraph {
    margin-top: 30px;
    margin-bottom: 40px;
  }

  .kitchen-quote-button {
    display: inline-flex;
    align-items: center;
    background-color: #000000;
    color: #ffffff;
    padding: 10px 20px;
    text-decoration: none;
    font-size: 12px;
    transition: background-color 0.3s ease;
    border: none; 
    cursor: pointer;
  }

  .kitchen-quote-button:hover {
    background-color: #333333;
  }

  .kitchen-quote-button .arrow-right {
    margin-left: 10px;
    font-size: 1.2em;
  }

  .kitchen-remodeling-image-column {
    flex: 1;
    display: flex;
    justify-content: center;
    align-items: flex-start;
  }

  .kitchen-main-image {
    max-width: 80%; 
    height: auto;
    display: block;
    box-shadow: 0 10px 30px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.1);
    border-radius: 8px; 
  }

  .section-color {
    background-color: #f1f2eb;
  }

  .ticker-text-wrapper {
    width: 100%;
    background-color: #f1f2eb;
    font-family: "Host Grotesk", sans-serif;
    border-bottom: 1px solid #adadad;
    color: #333333;
    padding: 40px 0;
    font-size: 30px;
    font-weight: 400;
    overflow: hidden; 
    white-space: nowrap; 
    box-sizing: border-box;
  }

  .ticker-text-container {
    display: inline-block;
    animation: scroll-left 100s linear infinite;
  }

  .ticker-item {
    padding-right: 50px;
    position: relative;
    padding-left: 20px;
  }

  .ticker-item::before {
    content: "";
    display: inline-block;
    width: 5px;
    height: 5px;
    background-color: #333333;
    border-radius: 50%;
    position: absolute;
    left: 5px;
    top: 50%;
    transform: translateY(-50%);
  }

  @keyframes scroll-left {
    0% {
      transform: translateX(0%);
    }
    100% {
      transform: translateX(-100%);
    }
  }

  .kitchen-remodeling-info-row {
    display: flex;
    width: 100%;
    background-color: #f1f2eb; 
  }

  .kitchen-remodeling-info-image {
    flex: 1;
    width: 100%; 
    height: auto; 
    max-width: 100%;
    object-fit: cover; 
    box-shadow: 0 10px 30px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.1);
    border-radius: 8px;
  }

  .kitchen-remodeling-info-content {
    flex: 1;
    color: #333333;
    display: flex;
    flex-direction: column;
    justify-content: center;
    padding: 0 100px;

    h2 {
      display: block;
      max-width: 550px; 
      font-family: "DM Sans", sans-serif;
      font-size: 3.5em;
      margin-bottom: 20px;
      color: #000000;
      line-height: 1.2;
      font-weight: 600;
      margin-right: auto; 
      margin-left: 0; 
    }

    p {
      display: block;
      max-width: 550px; 
      font-family: "DM Sans", sans-serif;
      line-height: 1.5;
      font-size: 14px;
      margin-bottom: 20px;
      color: #555555;
      margin-right: auto;
      margin-left: 0;
    }
  }

  @media (max-width: 1024px) {
    .kitchen-remodeling-content-wrapper {
      flex-direction: column;
      align-items: center; 
      gap: 50px; 
      padding: 0 30px; 
    }

    .kitchen-remodeling-text-column {
      max-width: 100%; 
      text-align: center; 
      padding: 0 15px; 
      box-sizing: border-box;
      align-items: center; 
    }

    .kitchen-remodeling-title {
      font-size: 3.5em; 
      width: auto; 
      margin-right: 0; 
      margin-left: auto;
      margin-right: auto; 
      margin-bottom: 30px; 
      max-width: 90%; 
      line-height: 1.1; 
    }

    .kitchen-remodeling-paragraph {
      font-size: 15px; 
      text-align: center; 
      max-width: 90%; 
      margin-left: auto;
      margin-right: auto;
    }

    .kitchen-remodeling-list {
      text-align: left; 
      display: block; 
      margin-left: auto; 
      margin-right: auto;
      max-width: 90%; 
    }
    .kitchen-remodeling-list li {
      padding-left: 25px; 
      text-align: left; 
      font-size: 15px; 
    }
    .kitchen-remodeling-list li::before {
      left: 5px; 
    }

    .kitchen-quote-button {
      margin: 0 auto; 
      font-size: 14px;
      padding: 15px 30px;
    }

    .kitchen-remodeling-image-column {
      width: 100%; 
      max-width: 600px; 
      margin: 0 auto; 
    }

    .kitchen-main-image {
      max-width: 100%; 
    }

    .ticker-text-wrapper {
      padding: 30px 0; 
      font-size: 24px; 
    }

    .kitchen-remodeling-info-row {
      flex-direction: column; 
    }

    .kitchen-remodeling-info-content {
      padding: 40px 30px; 
      align-items: center; 

      h2 {
        font-size: 2.5em; 
        max-width: 90%; 
        text-align: center; 
        margin-left: auto;
        margin-right: auto;
      }
      p {
        font-size: 15px; 
        max-width: 90%; 
        text-align: center; 
        margin-left: auto;
        margin-right: auto;
      }
    }
    .kitchen-remodeling-info-image {
        max-width: 100%; 
        margin: 0 auto; 
    }
  }

  @media (max-width: 768px) {
    .kitchen-remodeling-section-container {
      padding: 50px 0; 
    }

    .kitchen-remodeling-content-wrapper {
      gap: 40px; 
      padding: 0 15px; 
    }

    .kitchen-remodeling-text-column {
      padding: 0 10px; 
    }

    .kitchen-remodeling-title {
      font-size: 2.8em; 
      margin-bottom: 25px; 
    }

    .kitchen-remodeling-paragraph,
    .kitchen-remodeling-list li {
      font-size: 14px; 
      line-height: 1.5;
    }
    .kitchen-remodeling-paragraph.last-paragraph {
        margin-bottom: 30px;
    }

    .kitchen-remodeling-list li::before {
      left: 0px; 
      top: 0.6em;
    }

    .kitchen-quote-button {
      padding: 12px 25px;
      font-size: 13px;
    }

    .ticker-text-wrapper {
      padding: 25px 0;
      font-size: 20px;
    }

    .kitchen-remodeling-info-content {
      padding: 30px 20px; 
      h2 {
        font-size: 2em; 
      }
      p {
        font-size: 14px; 
      }
    }
  }

  @media (max-width: 480px) {
    .kitchen-remodeling-section-container {
      padding: 40px 0;
    }

    .kitchen-remodeling-content-wrapper {
      gap: 30px;
      padding: 0 10px;
    }

    .kitchen-remodeling-text-column {
      padding: 0 5px;
    }

    .kitchen-remodeling-title {
      font-size: 2.2em; 
      margin-bottom: 20px;
      line-height: 1.1;
    }

    .kitchen-remodeling-paragraph,
    .kitchen-remodeling-list li {
      font-size: 13px; 
      line-height: 1.5;
    }
    .kitchen-remodeling-paragraph.last-paragraph {
        margin-bottom: 20px;
    }

    .kitchen-remodeling-list li {
      padding-left: 20px;
    }
    .kitchen-remodeling-list li::before {
      left: 0px;
      top: 0.6em;
    }

    .kitchen-quote-button {
      padding: 10px 20px;
      font-size: 12px;
    }

    .ticker-text-wrapper {
      padding: 20px 0;
      font-size: 18px;
    }

    .kitchen-remodeling-info-content {
      padding: 20px 15px; 
      h2 {
        font-size: 1.8em; 
      }
      p {
        font-size: 13px; 
      }
    }
  }
</style>
